criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        . Age ≥18 years;

          -  Provision of written, informed consent;

          -  Untreated, HIV infected patients with CD4+ T cell counts 350 cells/µL or less;

          -  Treatment naïve or off ART for ≥12 months;

          -  Intention to commence cART that would be expected to reduce viral load by one log or
             greater

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Inability to give written informed consent;

          -  Any condition which the treating physician feels would compromise the ability of the
             patient to participate in the study.
